name: PHPScriptGen
short_description: PHPScriptGen is a powerful online tool that can automatically generates fully functional codes for your PHP/MySQL applications. You can create completed CRUD (Create, Retrieve Update and Delete) scripts within ten minutes. Thus it can save you a lot of time wasted on repetitive coding. The generated codes can be easily understood and further customized. It is designed for both beginners and veteran programmers. This amazing tool is completely FREE for both commercial & non-commercial use.
summary: PHPScriptGen – Free online PHP code generator for MySQL
